highlights.text: “八方來財(Stacks from All Sides)” by 攬佬SKAI ISYOURGOD has been on Viral Songs Vietnam the longest, at 184 days straight.
“good girls” by Josie Edwards is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Vietnam at #12.
DPR IAN has the most spots on Viral Songs Vietnam. “Don't Go Insane” is the highest at #7.
“this is what falling in love feels like - Multilingual” by Kitsui Akira is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Vietnam, up 19 spots at #79.
